name: Killing TikTok: Just go Fast& furious- kill the Big Ball
name_original: Killing TikTok: Just go Fast& furious- kill the Big Ball
description:
Jump on the platforms and killl robos with the game's Fast pace. Just a small Game                                                The Boss enemy is the TikTok (Big ball), end it##

WASD To MOVE
SPACE BAR To Jump
Click to shoot
//
*To jump Higher* :You can press Jump upto 4 times after touching the ground once.
Press 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 (Lower to higher) To decrease or increase Game Overall Graphics Quality and improve performance. Press 1 (One) to get *High FrameRate & No Lag*
R to Restart
H for HDR mode On/Off
P to Pause
Numlock keys: num1, num2, num3, num4 (Lower To Higher) Press these for video Resolution of the game.

F11 to minimize full view and then press windows to  see your mouse pointer

This Is my first unreal Engine game, so I hope you may like it.
Subscribe AsAsaniManiK on YouTube. Mail: emanikchannel10@gmail.com
//

 Lure in the fast pace  & kill the Boss

Hint:Kill the giant boss by hitting on the  man's face in the ball (Mr.AM.SD).
